$ PowerShell: the preference variable $verbosePreference
@ $verbosePreference

The value of the `$verbosePreference` → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference[preference variable] determines what happens when the
→ Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/verbose/write[`write-verbose`] cmdlet is invoked.

`$verbosePreference` can be assigned any value of the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Management/Automation/ActionPreference[`System.Management.Automation.ActionPreference`] enum.
